WEBVTT

00:00:57.039 --> 00:00:58.039
You killed two people

00:00:58.399 --> 00:00:59.439
To avoid being discovered

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:01.039
For the month that followed

00:01:01.759 --> 00:01:03.880
You hid in the air ducts of this villa

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:29.120
Before that

00:01:29.480 --> 00:01:30.640
Tan Tian clearly mentioned

00:01:30.959 --> 00:01:32.280
Feeling like he was being watched

00:01:32.439 --> 00:01:33.640
And hearing strange noises

00:01:33.959 --> 00:01:35.599
Don't you think there's something wrong with this house?

00:01:37.239 --> 00:01:38.000
As soon as you walk in

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:39.560
It makes you feel very uncomfortable

00:01:39.879 --> 00:01:40.159
Ghost

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:41.200
And Ma Shan often sees ghosts

00:01:41.359 --> 00:01:42.079
Auntie Ma Shan

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:43.879
It was actually you

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:44.480
There's a ghost

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:45.480
Don't be afraid

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:47.079
There are no ghosts

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:52.079
It's her

00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:53.760
She is the ghost

00:01:54.319 --> 00:01:55.280
She is the ghost

00:01:55.599 --> 00:01:56.879
She is Madam's little sister

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:58.599
She is the ghost

00:01:59.120 --> 00:01:59.920
Madam instructed

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:00.959
That you need to take your medicine on time

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:03.000
Let me take you back to your room to rest, okay?

00:02:04.239 --> 00:02:04.879
Okay

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:06.319
Please follow me, you two

00:02:06.519 --> 00:02:08.000
I'll take you to your respective rooms

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:09.599
Ghost

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:11.280
She is the ghost

00:02:11.719 --> 00:02:12.599
She is a ghost

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:13.919
Ms. Li

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:18.400
Is this house haunted?

00:02:22.199 --> 00:02:23.840
Humans fear ghosts, ghosts fear humans

00:02:24.599 --> 00:02:26.280
Whether it's a fake ghost or a real one

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.360
In my opinion

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:29.080
Humans are always the scariest

00:02:32.199 --> 00:02:33.120
When I was certain that inside the Sky Tower

00:02:33.240 --> 00:02:34.439
There was another person

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:37.360
I guessed that you weren't dead

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:42.520
Do you believe in ghosts?

00:02:44.479 --> 00:02:45.960
I actually hope ghosts are real

00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:47.039
That way

00:02:48.039 --> 00:02:50.439
Perhaps we sisters could meet again

00:02:52.319 --> 00:02:53.080
Aren't you afraid?

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:55.240
I am

00:02:55.879 --> 00:02:57.759
But humans are scarier

00:02:59.439 --> 00:03:00.159
The ring

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:01.240
Why do you have it?

00:03:02.719 --> 00:03:04.120
I found it at my door last night

00:03:05.199 --> 00:03:06.520
I think the person who dropped this ring

00:03:07.159 --> 00:03:08.960
Is the same one who took Fang Qiu's necklace

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:12.319
Who would know about these things?

00:03:13.199 --> 00:03:13.960
And actually, your little sister

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.560
Has also been buying time for you

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:16.800
To find the entrance to the secret room

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:18.280
If it weren't for you

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:20.719
Ma Shan wouldn't have acted against Fang Qiu so soon

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:23.400
And driving Zhao Qihai insane

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:25.039
Was all your doing

00:03:25.199 --> 00:03:26.080
Ghost!

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:27.800
I climbed into the air ducts to investigate

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:29.120
It was unusually clean inside

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:31.479
As long as the police search carefully

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.919
I believe they will find your biological traces

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:35.840
You knew that Zhao Qishan, inside this villa,

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:37.080
Had hidden a huge amount of cash

00:03:37.439 --> 00:03:38.800
But you didn't know the exact location

00:03:40.599 --> 00:03:42.879
So you bribed Lawyer Luo to draft a will

00:03:43.919 --> 00:03:45.120
But the details within it

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:46.879
Even your little sister didn't know

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:49.879
To allow your little sister

00:03:50.039 --> 00:03:51.360
To inherit the estate naturally

00:03:51.919 --> 00:03:53.439
You also bribed Superintendent He Jiarong

00:03:54.159 --> 00:03:55.240
To have him close the case quickly

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:57.800
Qi Yuan, you're about to be transferred

00:03:58.120 --> 00:04:00.159
Leave the case to someone else

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:07.199
Taicheng's crime rate is dropping every year

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:08.800
Especially major crimes

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:10.680
There have been almost none in the last two years

00:04:11.039 --> 00:04:12.439
Suddenly having something like this happen

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:15.199
You and I have to think about the higher-ups

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:21.839
No, Chief He.

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:23.680
My transfer order hasn't come down yet.

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:24.920
Enough, Old Qi.

00:04:25.319 --> 00:04:26.399
As soon as you transfer away,

00:04:26.759 --> 00:04:29.199
I've decided to take charge of this case personally.

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:31.399
Actually, the case isn't that complicated.

00:04:31.959 --> 00:04:33.800
It's just Zhao Qishan's wife, Di Fu,

00:04:34.079 --> 00:04:34.680
killing her husband,

00:04:34.759 --> 00:04:36.439
then burning herself to death to escape punishment.

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:37.519
As for you,

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:39.560
go home and get ready.

00:04:41.279 --> 00:04:42.240
Once the notification comes down from above,

00:04:42.439 --> 00:04:43.680
I'll let you know immediately.

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:48.199
It's great to go to the big city and be a Superintendent.

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:49.600
As for things here,

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:51.839
don't you worry about them.

00:04:52.439 --> 00:04:54.040
This way, you can avenge yourself,

00:04:54.399 --> 00:04:56.160
and buy yourself enough time

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:57.600
to find this secret room

00:04:57.959 --> 00:04:59.680
and take the massive amount of cash to escape.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:01.560
If I kill you,

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.360
no one will know I'm still alive.

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:05.519
Sister.

00:05:06.279 --> 00:05:07.240
I beg you.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:08.920
Don't kill anyone else.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:10.759
I'm sorry.

00:05:12.199 --> 00:05:13.600
I can't turn back now.

00:05:18.639 --> 00:05:20.319
Di Fu, don't move.

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:22.439
Give me the gun.

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:27.000
Give it here!

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:28.319
And you,

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:29.920
behave yourself.

00:05:31.959 --> 00:05:32.639
Di Fu.

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:34.480
You Witch, sure enough, you're not dead.

00:05:35.399 --> 00:05:36.920
You set me up,

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:38.959
trying to take all my money for yourself, huh?

00:05:47.040 --> 00:05:47.600
Sister.

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:20.319
Sister.

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:53.319
Get up.

00:06:57.319 --> 00:06:57.800
Move.

00:07:14.399 --> 00:07:15.360
Lin Niannian's body,

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:16.399
we found it.

00:07:28.560 --> 00:07:29.560
Fang Qiu confessed.

00:07:30.399 --> 00:07:32.240
The body was buried in an abandoned factory in the suburbs.

00:07:35.800 --> 00:07:37.399
Tan Tian, Zhao Qihai, A Si...

00:07:37.720 --> 00:07:38.560
they've all been arrested.

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:43.720
Zhao Qishan used the group as a front

00:07:44.319 --> 00:07:46.399
for online fraud. All the criminal evidence

00:07:47.279 --> 00:07:48.759
is now in our possession.

00:07:49.399 --> 00:07:50.120
Behave yourself.

00:07:52.639 --> 00:07:53.040
Get up.

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:53.720
Move.

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:55.959
The industrial park in Qingshan has also been sealed off.

00:07:57.199 --> 00:07:58.519
And the protective umbrella behind them

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:00.800
has been successfully taken down.

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:05.319
Everyone who committed crimes

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:08.279
will not escape the sanctions of the law.